1
00:00:04,556 --> 00:00:08,879
If I can get beyond the ego level
of being annoyed,

2
00:00:08,879 --> 00:00:13,050
then I can understand, whatever anyone
may say, think, do, whatever,

3
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:14,385
Guru Mahārāj would say,

4
00:00:14,385 --> 00:00:17,100
“You can trace it back
to the centre of the Infinite”,

5
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:19,684
[How to See Kṛṣṇa?]

6
00:00:19,684 --> 00:00:22,727
at the central conception 
of the Infinite.

7
00:00:22,727 --> 00:00:27,102
And that always means
Kṛṣṇa, Rādhā–Kṛṣṇa,

8
00:00:27,102 --> 00:00:34,691
Their chit-līlāmṛtam:
pastimes, divine abode, forms etc.

9
00:00:35,261 --> 00:00:39,432
The heart, 
the deep heart’s core.

10
00:00:39,432 --> 00:00:44,183
So the heart, under the influence
of love and affection for Kṛṣṇa,

11
00:00:44,183 --> 00:00:49,168
can see Kṛṣṇa properly.

12
00:00:49,168 --> 00:00:51,685
Hare Kṛṣṇa.

